                 Hey, everybody!

02:38.391 --> 02:40.526
I have the most wonderful news. 

02:40.593 --> 02:41.560
You got a job?                  

02:41.628 --> 02:43.762
         I have a job.          
                             Oh.

02:43.830 --> 02:44.830
I'm sorry.                      

